    <h1 class="mb-6">Lovable and Base44 vs AI Optimised Websites</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mb-8">By Adam Parker | Updated April 2026</p>

    <div class="bg-off-white border-l-3 border-l-teal rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
      <p class="text-[15px] text-teal font-medium leading-relaxed m-0">** AI-powered site builders create impressive prototypes quickly but fundamentally fail at AI search optimisation, whilst purpose-built static sites deliver superior performance for both search engines and AI crawlers.

